Package: MixMatrix
Type: Package
Title: Functions for Matrix Distributions
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-06-16
Authors@R: c(person(c("Geoffrey", "Thompson"),email="gzthompson@gmail.com",
          role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0003-2436-8822')))
Description: LDA and QDA for variate normal and T. 
          Sampling and density for matrix variate normal, t, and inverted 
          t-distributions. ML fitting for matrix variate normal and t-distributions
          including some restrictions on the parameters.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
